metadata.name: remains of the day
metadata.description: I took this image at Shiprock Monument in July 2022 as the light left. I took a several-day solo trip to process my recent crazy life events, and this was my first stop. While I did make more traditional pictures from the Shiprock, this one speaks to my feelings of sadness that were prominent at the time.
